---
// CAPCS Core Ingredient: Science meets beauty
---

<section id="science" class="section science">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="science-header reveal reveal-rise">
      <div class="science-accent-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <h2 class="science-title">贻贝钙肽CAPCS<sup>®</sup> 凯普斯泰</h2>
      <p class="science-subtitle">全球首创外用钙离子舒缓技术</p>
    </div>

    <div class="science-content reveal reveal-rise">
      <div class="science-image-col">
        <img src="/assets/capcs-ingredient.png" alt="CAPCS® 钙离子舒缓技术成分示意" class="science-image" />
      </div>

      <div class="science-cols-col">
        <div class="science-col">
          <span class="science-col-number" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
          <h3 class="science-col-title">30 秒快速止痒</h3>
          <p class="science-col-body">临床验证止痒速度优于弱效激素（氢化可的松），效果等同于弱效激素。切断"搔抓恶性循环"，从根源缓解皮肤问题。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="science-col">
          <span class="science-col-number" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
          <h3 class="science-col-title">13 年自主研发</h3>
          <p class="science-col-body">由生物学博士后团队研发，纯物理回流反渗技术萃取。发表于《中华皮肤科杂志》与 SCI 期刊，机理与临床双重验证。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="science-col">
          <span class="science-col-number" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
          <h3 class="science-col-title">五维金标准安全</h3>
          <p class="science-col-body">无激素、无抗生素、无防腐剂。经口无毒、入眼无刺激、人体斑贴无刺激、多次皮肤刺激无刺激、4000+ 争议成分不添加。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="science-data reveal reveal-rise">
      <div class="science-data-item">
        <span class="science-data-value">79%</span>
        <span class="science-data-label">止痒有效率</span>
      </div>
      <div class="science-data-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="science-data-item">
        <span class="science-data-value">67%</span>
        <span class="science-data-label">特应性皮炎治疗有效率</span>
      </div>
      <div class="science-data-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="science-data-item">
        <span class="science-data-value">6×</span>
        <span class="science-data-label">提高激素有效率</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .science {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding-top: var(--space-6xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-6xl);
  }

  .science-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .science-accent-line {
    width: 40px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--color-brand);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-lg);
  }

  .science-title {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 200;
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .science-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-text-soft);
  }

  /* ── Two-column split: image + editorial ── */
  .science-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4xl);
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .science-image-col {
    position: sticky;
    top: 120px;
  }

  .science-image {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .science-col {
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
  }

  .science-col + .science-col {
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .science-col-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-widest);
    color: var(--color-brand);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .science-col-title {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
  }

  .science-col-body {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-soft);
  }

  /* ── Data bar ── */
  .science-data {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
  }

  .science-data-item {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .science-data-value {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 200;
    color: var(--color-brand-dark);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .science-data-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 20ch;
  }

  .science-data-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--color-border);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .science-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-2xl);
    }

    .science-image-col {
      position: static;
    }

    .science-image {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .science-data {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }
    .science-data-divider {
      width: 48px;
      height: 1px;
    }
  }
</style>
